			      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
				        <ab>(This) image of the Bhagavant was established by the
                        <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">śrāmaṇaka</foreign> Rāhula,
                    pupil of master Dharmadeva, beloved pupil of master
                    Maudgalyāyana, for the attainment of the supreme knowledge
                    by all beings. What merit is here, may that be for (all)
                    beings.</ab>
			      </div>
